reviewText: The Warmaster Josh Barnett gives a fantastic look at the basics of catch wrestling, demonstrating ans explaining techniques with ease, bjj exponents look out cause after watching this, catch wrestling has found many holes in your so called unstoppable art:)

This will speak volumes to you. He's not subtle, he teaches you he teaches you. You learn it like that. It's Josh Barnett and Erik Paulson here and there. Hell of a DVD. The only sad part is that the audio kinda sucks, but you can't win 'em all huh.
